---
layout: default
title: "About Us — Apex Agency"
description: "Meet the team behind the world's most trusted growth partner for premium brands."
permalink: /about/
page_label: "About"
page_subtitle: "We're strategists, creatives, engineers, and dreamers — united by a single mission: engineering exponential growth."
---

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     OUR STORY
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="story" class="section scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <div data-animate>
        <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Born from a Bold Idea</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body text-midnight/70 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            In 2015, our founder Alexander Sterling noticed a glaring gap in the 
            market: Fortune 500 brands had access to world-class growth strategies, 
            but ambitious mid-market and premium brands were left navigating a 
            fragmented landscape of agencies that promised everything but delivered little.
          </p>
          <p>
            Apex Agency was built to close that gap. We assembled a team of 
            top-tier talent from McKinsey, Google, Wieden+Kennedy, Amazon, and 
            Spotify — people who had engineered growth at the highest levels — 
            and gave them a single mission: democratize enterprise-grade growth 
            for brands that dared to dream bigger.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, we're a team of 85+ strategists, creatives, engineers, and 
            data scientists spanning three continents. We've partnered with 
            over 200 brands across 15+ countries, generating $2.4B+ in client 
            revenue and earning 50+ industry awards along the way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative" data-animate data-delay="200">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-lg bg-midnight overflow-hidden shadow-elevated">
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-gold/20 to-midnight flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center p-8">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"/>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-cloud/60 text-body-sm">Apex Agency — Culture Video</p>
              <p class="text-cloud/40 text-caption mt-2">Click to play</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-gold/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     VALUES
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="values" class="section-dark relative overflow-hidden scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-noise"></div>
  <div class="container-page relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-animate>
      <span class="section-label">Our Values</span>
      <h2 class="section-title-light">Principles That Drive Us</h2>
      <p class="section-desc section-desc-light mx-auto">
        Six core values that guide every decision, every partnership, and every
        pixel we produce.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8" data-animate>
      {% for value in team.values %}
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          {% case value.icon %}
          {% when 'eye' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/>
          </svg>
          {% when 'gem' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
          {% when 'rocket' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z"/>
          </svg>
          {% when 'handshake' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
          </svg>
          {% when 'sync' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
          </svg>
          {% when 'bullseye' %}
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
          {% endcase %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-heading font-semibold text-cloud mb-3">{{ value.title }}</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-cloud/50">{{ value.description }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     TEAM
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="team" class="section scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-animate>
      <span class="section-label">Our Team</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Meet the People Behind the Growth</h2>
      <p class="section-desc mx-auto">
        85+ brilliant minds across three continents, united by a shared obsession 
        with engineering exponential growth for premium brands.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-12" data-animate>
      {% for member in team.team %}
      <div class="team-card group">
        <div class="relative mx-auto w-40 h-40 mb-6">
          <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-midnight to-midnight-light flex items-center justify-center shadow-soft">
            <span class="font-display text-display-lg font-bold text-gold">{{ member.name | split: ' ' | first | slice: 0 }}{{ member.name | split: ' ' | last | slice: 0 }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-heading font-semibold">{{ member.name }}</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-gold font-medium mt-1">{{ member.role }}</p>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-midnight/50 mt-3 leading-relaxed">{{ member.bio | truncate: 150 }}</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mt-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
          {% if member.social.linkedin %}
          <a href="{{ member.social.linkedin }}" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-midnight/10 flex items-center justify-center text-midnight/50 hover:bg-gold hover:text-midnight transition-colors" aria-label="{{ member.name }} on LinkedIn">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          </a>
          {% endif %}
          {% if member.social.twitter %}
          <a href="{{ member.social.twitter }}" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-midnight/10 flex items-center justify-center text-midnight/50 hover:bg-gold hover:text-midnight transition-colors" aria-label="{{ member.name }} on Twitter">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.953 4.57a10 10 0 01-2.825.775 4.958 4.958 0 002.163-2.723c-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184a4.92 4.92 0 00-8.384 4.482C7.69 8.095 4.067 6.13 1.64 3.162a4.822 4.822 0 00-.666 2.475c0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096a4.904 4.904 0 01-2.228-.616v.06a4.923 4.923 0 003.946 4.827 4.996 4.996 0 01-2.212.085 4.936 4.936 0 004.604 3.417 9.867 9.867 0 01-6.102 2.105c-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067a13.995 13.995 0 007.557 2.209c9.053 0 13.998-7.496 13.998-13.985 0-.21 0-.42-.015-.63A9.935 9.935 0 0024 4.59z"/></svg>
          </a>
          {% endif %}
          {% if member.social.instagram %}
          <a href="{{ member.social.instagram }}" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-midnight/10 flex items-center justify-center text-midnight/50 hover:bg-gold hover:text-midnight transition-colors" aria-label="{{ member.name }} on Instagram">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 0C8.74 0 8.333.015 7.053.072 5.775.132 4.905.333 4.14.63c-.789.306-1.459.717-2.126 1.384S.935 3.35.63 4.14C.333 4.905.131 5.775.072 7.053.012 8.333 0 8.74 0 12s.015 3.667.072 4.947c.06 1.277.261 2.148.558 2.913.306.788.717 1.459 1.384 2.126.667.666 1.336 1.079 2.126 1.384.766.296 1.636.499 2.913.558C8.333 23.988 8.74 24 12 24s3.667-.015 4.947-.072c1.277-.06 2.148-.262 2.913-.558.788-.306 1.459-.718 2.126-1.384.666-.667 1.079-1.335 1.384-2.126.296-.765.499-1.636.558-2.913.06-1.28.072-1.687.072-4.947s-.015-3.667-.072-4.947c-.06-1.277-.262-2.149-.558-2.913-.306-.789-.718-1.459-1.384-2.126C21.319 1.347 20.651.935 19.86.63c-.765-.297-1.636-.499-2.913-.558C15.667.012 15.26 0 12 0zm0 2.16c3.203 0 3.585.016 4.85.071 1.17.055 1.805.249 2.227.415.562.217.96.477 1.382.896.419.42.679.819.896 1.381.164.422.36 1.057.413 2.227.057 1.266.07 1.646.07 4.85s-.015 3.585-.074 4.85c-.061 1.17-.256 1.805-.421 2.227-.224.562-.479.96-.899 1.382-.419.419-.824.679-1.38.896-.42.164-1.065.36-2.235.413-1.274.057-1.649.07-4.859.07-3.211 0-3.586-.015-4.859-.074-1.171-.061-1.816-.256-2.236-.421-.569-.224-.96-.479-1.379-.899-.421-.419-.69-.824-.9-1.38-.165-.42-.359-1.065-.42-2.235-.045-1.26-.061-1.649-.061-4.844 0-3.196.016-3.586.061-4.861.061-1.17.255-1.814.42-2.234.21-.57.479-.96.9-1.381.419-.419.81-.689 1.379-.898.42-.166 1.051-.361 2.221-.421 1.275-.045 1.65-.06 4.859-.06l.045.03z"/></svg>
          </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
          {% for expertise in member.expertise %}
          <span class="badge bg-midnight/5 text-midnight/60 text-caption">{{ expertise }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     AWARDS
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="awards" class="section bg-cloud-dark/30 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container-page">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-animate>
      <span class="section-label">Recognition</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Awards & Accolades</h2>
      <p class="section-desc mx-auto">
        Our work has been recognized by the most prestigious organizations in our industry.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-animate>
      {% for award in team.awards %}
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-lg bg-white shadow-soft">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-heading font-semibold">{{ award.name }}</h3>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-midnight/50 mt-1">{{ award.organization }}, {{ award.year }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

